verse = \lyricmode {
  Save me, O God, by your great name,
and by your pow -- er vin -- di -- cate me.
I am be -- set by those who hate me;
God, hear my prayer: your help I claim.
Men who do not keep you in sight
at -- tack me, seek -- ing my de -- struc -- tion.
Come to my aid with your pro -- tec -- tion;
save me from those who plot and fight.
}
